<details>
<summary>Days 1-20: Python Foundations Refresh (Web-Focused) + Cert: PCAP (Python Institute, $295 paid, entry-level hiring boost)</summary>
<ul>
  <li>Days 1-3: Variables, types, strings + <a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/python">Coursera Python for Everybody (free audit)</a></li>
  <li>Days 4-6: Lists, loops, functions + <a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/learn/scientific-computing-with-python/">freeCodeCamp Python (free)</a></li>
  <li>Day 7: Weekly Test 1 + Review</li>
  <li>Days 8-10: Dicts, sets, file I/O + <a href="https://docs.python.org/3/tutorial/">Official Python Tutorial (free)</a></li>
  <li>Days 11-13: OOP, exceptions + <a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/complete-python-bootcamp/">Udemy 100 Days Python ($15 paid, cert)</a></li>
  <li>Day 14: Weekly Test 2</li>
  <li>Days 15-20: Modules, virtual envs, Git + <a href="https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2">Git Book (free)</a>; Cert prep: PCAP practice</li>
</ul>
</details>

